		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />PAR = pixel aspect ratio
<br />8.0/7.0 = 8.0 divided by 7.0 = about 1.143
<br />
<br />256 * scale_value * PAR = 292x240, 585x480, 878x720

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


